<noinclude>
==Documentation==
Renders the franchise page sidebar with structured data pulled from Semantic MediaWiki properties.

This template is called automatically by <code><nowiki>{{FranchiseEnd}}</nowiki></code>.

===Sections===
# '''Franchise details''' - Name, game count, first game, aliases
# '''Related content''' - Accordion sections for Characters, Locations, Concepts, Objects, People

===SMW Properties Used===
* <code>Has name</code> - Franchise title
* <code>Has aliases</code> - Alternative names
* <code>Has games</code> - Game links (also queried via inverse)
* <code>Has characters</code> - Character links
* <code>Has locations</code> - Location links
* <code>Has concepts</code> - Concept links
* <code>Has objects</code> - Object links
</noinclude><includeonly>
<div class="gb-franchise-sidebar">
<div class="gb-sidebar-section">
<div class="gb-sidebar-section-header">Franchise details</div>
<div class="gb-sidebar-section-content">
<dl class="gb-franchise-details">

<dt>Name</dt>
<dd>{{#show:{{FULLPAGENAME}}|?Has name|default={{SUBPAGENAME}}}}</dd>

<dt>Features</dt>
<dd>{{#ask: [[Has franchises::{{FULLPAGENAME}}]] [[Category:Games]]
  |format=count
}} games</dd>
<dd class="gb-games-view-link">[{{canonicalurl:{{FULLPAGENAME}}}}#Games view all â†’]</dd>

{{#ask: [[Has franchises::{{FULLPAGENAME}}]] [[Category:Games]]
  |?Has name=name
  |format=template
  |template=FranchiseFirstGame
  |named args=yes
  |link=none
  |limit=1
  |sort=Has release date
  |order=asc
  |searchlabel=
  |default=
}}

{{#show:{{FULLPAGENAME}}
  |?Has aliases
  |format=list
  |link=none
  |default=
  |intro=<dt>Aliases</dt><dd>
  |outro=</dd>
}}

